    "is_free": false,
    "description": "2672年，地球资源全面枯竭，<br>人类远征军前往宇宙探索异星寻求生机，<br>不料遇到虫潮攻击，双方大战在所难免。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904190/extras/44441107fc9e25359b362792f07afbab.avif?t=1682056141\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><br>《异星前哨》是集即时策略、模拟经营、宏大战斗、英雄成长、roguelike等元素于一身的国产科幻生存RTS游戏。玩家需建立自己的前哨基地，不断发展科技和人口，将基地及周边建设成牢不可破的防御带。同时，需要时刻警惕并抵御四周袭来的“异形”或主动出击，直至最终消灭它们。<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904190/extras/775fea017216da31e1b434d494aabd63.avif?t=1682056141\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><br>游戏传承RTS经典玩法，并将生存模拟、即时战略有机融合。你会从上帝视角建设基地，持续经营，发展军队。在异星虫潮的奇袭或猛攻下，寻求生存。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904190/extras/5df0d6656226cb1ad4f87736e3d50b89.poster.avif?t=1682056141\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904190/extras/5df0d6656226cb1ad4f87736e3d50b89.webm?t=1682056141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904190/extras/5df0d6656226cb1ad4f87736e3d50b89.mp4?t=1682056141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904190/extras/8cbf84d93a0a45e4c5269f23219abefe.avif?t=1682056141\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><br>每个英雄拥有完全不一样的玩法和策略，且各具独特兵种、建筑、技能树！远程消耗、近战爆发、连协作战等，各种套路玩法总有你的喜爱！前方小心，博德英雄的烈焰冲击！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904190/extras/920f1d147abf211b12b81d81fefc90c2.poster.avif?t=1682056141\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904190/extras/920f1d147abf211b12b81d81fefc90c2.webm?t=1682056141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904190/extras/920f1d147abf211b12b81d81fefc90c2.mp4?t=1682056141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904190/extras/ed13d4d6cc17ab511e20510298cf078f.avif?t=1682056141\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><br>游戏多可同屏容纳100000作战单位不卡顿！面临数以万计的异形虫潮，使用有效策略、合理规划防线，痛快迎战，致命出击，摧枯拉朽般将敌人消灭殆尽，获得极致爽感体验！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904190/extras/c930dc742ac9059aec569f0ca61f014a.poster.avif?t=1682056141\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904190/extras/c930dc742ac9059aec569f0ca61f014a.webm?t=1682056141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904190/extras/c930dc742ac9059aec569f0ca61f014a.mp4?t=1682056141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904190/extras/2ea693e1cc239eef7789f2fa5107c900.avif?t=1682056141\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><br>游戏内容充实，不同局势策略组合繁多，获胜方法不止一种！<br>● 5大地图，戈壁、雪地、沼泽...各具专属机制规则，如昼夜天气、传送门；<br>● 20+种作战兵种，医疗兵、全能坦克、安保队员、执行者...属性功效各不相同；<br>● 60+种天赋技能，建筑加成、英雄专属能力、兵种强化...挑战无限可能；<br>● 70+种怪物异形，爆破种、虫后、噩梦飞龙、死亡菌菇...敌人超乎想象。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904190/extras/a8831a7446ba9737734d67beb6e2b028.poster.avif?t=1682056141\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904190/extras/a8831a7446ba9737734d67beb6e2b028.webm?t=1682056141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904190/extras/a8831a7446ba9737734d67beb6e2b028.mp4?t=1682056141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904190/extras/2c8b81036108153552d5f1ae75afd11f.avif?t=1682056141\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><br>编辑器上百模型组件随心使用，超多预置功能任意搭配，可自由设计玩法、任务、地图、事件等；<br>创意工坊支持编辑器地图一键上传同步，并可上传各类mod！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904190/extras/675e681cb703b13c10ca0ee99a84c0e5.avif?t=1682056141\" width=600 height=398 /></span>",
